MODULES TYPES

1. commands:- command
                         shell
                         script
                         raw

2. files:- copy
               file
               find
               lineinfile
                replace
                template

3. database:- mongodb
                      mysql
                     postgresql
                     proxysql

4. cloud:- amazon
                 azure
                 atomic
                 digitalocean
                 google
                 linode
                 vmware
                 smartos
5. windows:- Win_copy
                      Win_command
                      Win_domain
                      Win_file

6. system:- user
                   Group
                   Hostname
                   Make
                   Mount
                   Ping
                   Systemd
                   Service

1. command – Executes a command on a remote node
2. script – runs a local script on a remote node after trasferring it.
3. service – start, stop, restart services
